1
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:01,525
Immortals is different.

2
00:00:01,475 --> 00:00:03,466
It is an enterprise team you delegate to.

3
00:00:03,466 --> 00:00:07,333
You hand one manager your goal, in plain English — and it brings your ideas to life.

4
00:00:07,333 --> 00:00:13,458
The manager writes a real plan, picks the right specialists — a researcher, a critic, a coder, an experimenter — and runs them for you.

5
00:00:13,458 --> 00:00:16,525
You talk to one agent; a whole expert team does the work behind it.

6
00:00:16,525 --> 00:00:18,033
You delegate the task.

7
00:00:18,033 --> 00:00:19,683
You get back a finished result.

